DESCRIPTION: The time is up, you have not validated that you want to restore the invitations of the mentioned member (s).
NO_INVITES: Allows you to synchronize the server invitations with the bot database.
CONFIRM: Please confirm that you are sure you want to synchronize invitations from all server members with the database. Type ``-confirm`` to confirm or ``cancel`` to cancel.
CANCELLED: The synchronization of invitations for all members has been canceled.
SUCCESS: The invitations of all members have been synchronized.
TIMEOUT: The time is up, you have not validated that you want to synchronize the invitations of all the members of the server.
